title: Code Loops
description: Coding Blocks, Vadodara is organizing “CODE LOOPS”, a competitive coding contest in collaboration with MozGuj, DSC NUV, MSP and Xplora Club ITM.

title: Hack The Web
description: DSC NUV powered by Google and Microsoft Student Partner Program invites you to an exclusive meethub – Hack the Web. Hardik Mistry – Founder @ APPMATIC and a MICROSOFT MVP will be joining us to share his wisdom and industrial experience. He will also act as the judge of the Hack the Web - a website development competition.

title: GCP Crash Course
description: Developer Student Clubs Navrachana University in collaboration with Google Cloud Platform and Qwiklabs brought #GCPCrashCourse, which is the best way to get started with Google Cloud Platform. It was a month-long event where students had to complete the Crash Course within a month to be eligible for Goodies

title: Explore Machine Learning
description: Explore Machine Learning is a Google-sponsored program for university students to get started with Machine Learning. The curriculum offers 3 tracks of Machine Learning Content (Beginner, Intermediate, Advanced) and relies on university student facilitators to train other students on campus in a two-day hands-on workshop.

title: Flutter IO Extended
description: A viewing party wherein the Flutter IO Event was streamed for the students. A small session on how to integrate Agora with Flutter followed the stream.

title: No Light
description: It was a session on HTML and CSS where students were taught some basics and there was a Coding competition done where students had to make the same webpage as shown in the template without surfing the net or previewing the code on browser

title: MLH Local Host Python Programming
description: A session on basic fundamentals and Python was taken for Students, where they were taught Python and how it can be used for AI.
